headline: Lockheed Martin Adds IBM Granite to its Suite of Next-Generation AI Factory Tools
summary: Lockheed Martin, a longtime leader in harnessing artificial intelligence to boost defense and aerospace capabilities, is once again reshaping the future of AI-driven innovation. In a new collaboration, IBM's high-performing, enterprise-ready Granite large language models (LLMs) will be integrated into Lockheed Martin's AI Factory tools, which are accessed by more than 10,000 Lockheed Martin developers and engineers.
